=============================================
		Bomberman
=============================================

player 1 controls - red and blue costume
--------------------
Up Arrow     =  Up
Down Arrow   =  Down
Left Arrow   =  Left
Right arrow  =  Right
m            =  Plant Bomb

Player 2 controls - blue and green costume
--------------------
w      =  Up
s      =  Down
a      =  Left
d      =  Right
space  =  Plant Bomb

If you want to run the game you can run it using the bomberman jar file

latest version: v0.4